      "text": "Transition Actions:\n  Camera: dayCamera.Priority=0, nightCamera.Priority=10\n  Input map swap: DayPhase -> NightPhase (PLANNED)\n  Lighting: Color.Lerp(day->night, transitionSpeed)\n  Cursor: CursorLockMode.Locked, visible=false\n  GameEvents.DayPhaseCleanup() fires\n  DayPhaseHUD panel hides",
