      "updated": 1776348349724,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "State Change Flow:\n  Server: CurrentState.Value = newState\n  -> OnValueChanged callback fires\n  -> GameEvents.GameStateChanged(prev, cur)\n  -> All listeners react:\n     CameraManager, LightingManager,\n     DayPhaseHUD, CustomerSpawner, etc.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "State Change Flow:\n  Server: CurrentState.Value = newState\n  -> OnValueChanged callback fires\n  -> GameEvents.GameStateChanged(prev, cur)\n  -> All listeners react:\n     CameraManager, LightingManager,\n     DayPhaseHUD, CustomerSpawner, etc.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b09",
      "autoResize": true
    },
